 and author, who has a special interest in the Freedom of Information Act. He has written the book, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.uk/Freedom-Information-Practical-Guide-Journalists/dp/1138793213/\">Freedom of Information: A Practical Guide for Journalists</a>, and runs the <a href=\"http://www.foi.directory/\">FOI Directory</a> website.</p>\n<iframe style=\"float:left; max-width:100%;\" width=\"600px\" height=\"500px\" src=\"https://www.scribd.com/embeds/284174845/content?start_page=1&view_mode=scroll&access_key=key-3fIjjbSHnJfLyOnjSTHs&show_recommendations=true\" data-auto-height=\"false\" data-aspect-ratio=\"1.7790927021696252\" scrolling=\"no\" id=\"doc_98477\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>","excerpt":"You bring your lunch, we provide tea and coffee, an interesting talk, and enough time to get back to your desk.\r","language":"en","need_extended_font":false,"alternative_title":"","end_date":"2015-10-09T12:50:00+00:00","location":"Open Data Institute, 65 Clifton Street","start_date":"2015-10-09T12:00:00+00:00","booking_url":"https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/friday-lunchtime-lecture-open-wide-how-freedom-of-information-and-open-data-can-work-together-tickets-18430425900","hashtag":"ODIFridays","event_type":"event:lunchtime-lecture","organizations":[],"author":{}},"related_external_links":[],"related":[{"id":"https://contentapi.theodi.org/whats-apining-in-your-local-area-revealing-places-with-open-data.json","web_url":"http://theodi.org/lunchtime-lectures/whats-apining-in-your-local-area-revealing-places-with-open-data","slug":"whats-apining-in-your-local-area-revealing-places-with-open-data","title":"Friday lunchtime lecture: What’s ‘api’ning in your local area? Revealing places with open data","format":"event","updated_at":"2015-11-05T14:33:13+00:00","created_at":"2015-08-25T14:22:10+00:00","tag_ids":["event:lunchtime-lecture","lecture","local-government","geodata"],"extras":{"start_date":"2015-09-18T12:00:00+00:00","end_date":"2015-09-18T12:50:00+00:00","location":"